::Kaiser::
       He gets out of his seat at his station and takes his place next to 
Blackheart.  "What my esteemed commander forgets to mention is that some 
images appear there twice.  Apparently they don't take them down if you're 
only presumed dead and then found."  He smirks and glances at Blackheart.
